', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/127163/', '', 'Tinidazole, Pantoprazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Rabeprazole, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Rifabutin, Nizatidine, Ranitidine, Amoxicillin', 'Desipramine, Vilazodone, Maprotiline, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Amoxapine, More', 1767369485);
